how my puppy died my month old puppy died this past tuesday i posted something explaining the situation and i got a lot of negative feed back from some people telling me 'you shouldve taken him to the vet' 'animal abuser' and all sorts of other dumb stuff so tuesday nite i took him to someone who could tell me what went wrong the vet told me that marley was a healthy puppy all his shots no viruses diseases he died from 'spontaneous heart failure' for those of you who don't understand those terms his heart just randomly stopped beating for him the vet also told me that there wasn't too much i couldve done for him so for those who supported me thank you now i ask that you pray for my brother who just got into a car accident and is in the hospital my grandmother who just found a tumor in her neck i'm only posting this because a lot of people wanted to know how he died i said i'd find out and get back to everyone and to sensimllia are you the devil omg that is so sad i am an animal lover and i can understand how it feels when ppl think that you killed it or laugh u when you say something personal my grandma is on oxygen and my cat foxy has asthma so does my little bro so i will keep you in my prayers Pitaten Sin City Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma EastEnders Rabies Housebreaking Socialization Time Out of Mind Prostate cancer Friends Stomach cancer Series finale Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Theory of conduct Traumatic incident reduction One Tree Hill (TV series) Skinny Puppy Kodocha One Piece minor characters Blood on the Tracks Marilyn Monroe Myocardial infarction Shaggy dog story May 2005 in Australia and New Zealand Randomness Dog Ferret One Life to Live Pneumonia Oh My Goddess! Dog training YuYu Hakusho Stop Huntingdon Animal Cruelty Doctor Wily Knots Landing Dawson's Creek The Ashlee Simpson Show Vegeta History of As the World Turns (2000-present) Garfield Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Infantilism The Marshall Mathers LP Episodes of Lost (Season 1) The Cont